# assignment #

assignment statements
    unary assignment operators
        ++
        --

assignment as an expression
    while((ch=getchar()) != EOF) {...}
        1. ch=getchar() is carried out
        2. c != EOF is carried out

multiple assignment
    a, b, c = 10, 20, 30

mixed-mode assignment
    in ada, there is no assignment coercion

# closures #

subprogram and the referencing env where it was defined

object closure
    we can encapsulate our subroutine as a method of a simple object
        and let the onkects fields hold context for the method